ZH: 我喜欢骑摩托车去旅行。
EN: I like to travel on a motorcycle.

ZH: 他开着摩托车飞驰在马路上。
EN: He was speeding on his motorcycle on the road.

ZH: 我买了一辆新摩托车。
EN: I bought a new motorcycle.

ZH: 她学会了如何骑摩托车。
EN: She learned how to ride a motorcycle.

ZH: 这辆摩托车的引擎声很响。
EN: The engine of this motorcycle is very loud.

ZH: 他们去年夏天环游了欧洲，全程骑摩托车。
EN: They toured Europe last summer on motorcycles.

ZH: 我希望能在海滩上骑着摩托车。
EN: I hope to ride a motorcycle on the beach.

ZH: 摩托车是一种很自由的交通工具。
EN: Motorcycles are a very liberating mode of transportation.

ZH: 许多人梦想拥有一辆摩托车。
EN: Many people dream of owning a motorcycle.

ZH: 他是一个摩托车爱好者，有多辆收藏的经典摩托车。
EN: He is a motorcycle enthusiast, with several classic motorcycles in his collection.

ZH: 摩托车的速度可以很快。
EN: Motorcycles can go very fast.

ZH: 这边有摩托车停车处吗？
EN: Is there a motorcycle parking lot here?

ZH: 我觉得摩托车比汽车更方便。
EN: I think motorcycles are more convenient than cars.

ZH: 这座城市有很多人骑摩托车上班。
EN: Many people in this city ride motorcycles to work.

ZH: 这辆摩托车看起来非常酷。
EN: This motorcycle looks very cool.

ZH: 他每个周末都会骑着摩托车到乡间去。
EN: He rides his motorcycle to the countryside every weekend.

ZH: 这辆摩托车可以载两个人。
EN: This motorcycle can carry two people.

ZH: 摩托车比自行车快一些。
EN: Motorcycles are faster than bicycles.

ZH: 请戴好头盔再骑摩托车。
EN: Please wear a helmet when riding a motorcycle.

ZH: 摩托车比汽车更省油。
EN: Motorcycles are more fuel-efficient than cars.
